                        model="text-container-text"
                        modelFields="[text]"
                        name="Text Container Text"
                        text="&lt;p>There’s even more work being done to reach people around the world.&lt;br> AbbVie also partners with &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.sightsavers.org/&quot;>Sightsavers&lt;/a>, and the &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.iapb.org/&quot;>International Agency for the Prevention of Blindness&lt;/a>, a non-profit whose goal is to prevent avoidable blindness and save the sight of some of the world’s most vulnerable people.&lt;/p>"/>
